    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just the thing... it feels like a script. people say \"you matter\" because it's what you're supposed to say. but looking at my life, it feels so hollow. like i'm just taking up space that could be used for something else. if i just drifted away, there wouldn't even be a ripple. it's almost peaceful to think about just not existing anymore.",
